---
import Card from "../Card.astro";
---

<section id="next-section" class="py-20 px-8 pt-24 z-30 text-white relative">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
		<h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
			Art meets <span class="italic text-orange-500">systems</span>.
		</h2>
		<p class="text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto font-semibold">
			We're a creative systems studio — we design the strategy, tools, and
			workflows that turn ideas into repeatable storytelling. Photos and
			video are outputs, not the whole story: assets built to feed your
			channels and keep your message working overtime.
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mx-auto">
		<Card>
			<span class="badge badge-accent badge-lg">Visual Storytelling</span>
			<p class="font-semibold text-xl max-w-md mt-4">
				Every frame matters — and every asset should earn its keep. We
				capture moments with reuse in mind: media that's shot, tagged,
				and structured to plug into the workflows that tell your story
				consistently.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 lg:h-[500px]">
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
						src="/images/tourpass.png"
					/>
				</figure>
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden h-full">
					<img
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
						src="/images/tourpass.png"
					/>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</Card>

		<Card>
			<span class="badge badge-secondary badge-lg">Creative Systems</span>
			<p class="font-semibold text-xl max-w-md mt-4">
				Creativity deserves infrastructure. We design blueprints, build
				content engines, and stitch together the workflows, templates,
				and automations that stop creativity from getting stuck in chaos
				— and start making it repeatable, measurable, and fun.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 lg:h-[500px]">
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="h-full w-full object-cover"
						src="images/evolutionary-blades.png"
					/>
				</figure>
				<figure class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
					<img
						class="h-full w-full object-cover"
						src="images/evolutionary-blades.png"
					/>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</Card>
	</div>
</section>
